Package valorless.havenbags.datamodels

Class Data

java.lang.Object
valorless.havenbags.datamodels.Data
public class Data extends Object
Data model representing a HavenBag's persistent and runtime state. Includes identity (uuid/owner/creator), visual configuration (material, name, texture, custom model), inventory contents, feature flags (autopickup, weight, autosort, magnet, refill, whitelist/blacklist), and transient GUI/viewer state. Mutator methods generally mark the instance as changed for persistence.
